parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to jerk, hesitate, or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates when shifting gears
the vehicle jerks or lurches when accelerating
the vehicle loses power or stalls
the check engine light or transmission warning light illuminates
and the vehicle may not shift into gear or may shift erratically.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch master cylinder can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch hydraulic system can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Takata airbag inflator can cause the airbag to rupture, sending metal fragments into the passenger compartment, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The SRS warning light illuminates
the airbag deploys unexpectedly
the airbag does not deploy in a crash
the passenger side airbag warning light stays on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can cause the airbag to deploy unexpectedly, or not deploy in a crash, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The SRS warning light illuminates
the airbag deploys unexpectedly
the airbag does not deploy in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inadequate repair and customer service can cause frustration and delay in resolving the issue, which can lead to continued risk of injury or death.
symptoms: Difficulty in scheduling a repair
parts not available
dealer unable to repair
manufacturer unresponsive.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Premature Rusting of Frame and Subframe
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The premature rusting of the frame and subframe can lead to structural failure, compromising the vehicle's safety and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: Rusting of the frame and subframe
particularly on the passenger side
corrosion of the engine cradle
and rusting of the front passenger cross frame member.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of motor mounts can cause the engine to shift, leading to loss of control and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: Collapsed front and right front motor mounts
engine shifting
and unusual noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission problems can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Transmission slipping
downshifting without warning
and unusual noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Problems with the traction control system can cause the vehicle to lose traction, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Excessive wear on the driver's side front tire
slippage of the front driver's side tire during right turns
and unusual noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Wheel bearing failure can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Whirring noise
vibration
and unusual noises.
